    {
      "id": "s1-1",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "Getting started",
      "body": "```shell script\n$ screen\n```\n\n1\\. Press Ctrl-A D to detach session\n\n2\\. List all screen sessions\n\n```shell script\n$ screen -ls\n```\n\n3\\. Re-attach a screen Session\n\n```shell script\n$ screen -r <name/pid>\n```"
    },
